about.summary: In a stately, 100-year-old building, this classic hotel is a 9-minute walk from Westfield San Francisco Centre mall and 0.9 miles from the Cable Car Museum. Bright rooms have hardwood floors, and come with separate sitting areas. All have free WiFi, flat-screen TVs and coffeemakers; some have minifridges. Upgraded rooms and suites add bay windows. There's an upscale bistro and bar. Other amenities include an exercise room, and freebies such as bike rentals, and afternoon coffee and snacks. Dog beds, water bowls and pet treats are available (fee).

data.name: Hotel Fusion
data.full_address: Hotel Fusion, 140 Ellis St, San Francisco, CA 94102

about.summary: Surrounded by the shops, museums and restaurants of vibrant Union Square, this elegant hotel is a minute's walk from the Powell Street BART rail station, with connections to Muni trains and cable-car lines, and a 10-minute walk from the expansive Yerba Buena Gardens. Colorful rooms and junior suites for 1-4 guests feature Asian-inspired furniture and wall art, and come with flat-screen TVs, minifridges and designer toiletries. All rooms have ceiling fans and free Wi-Fi; some include air-conditioners. Amenities include an exercise room, a pan-Asian restaurant that serves dinner most nights and a lively 6,500-sq-ft lounge and nightclub.

about.summary: A 5-minute walk from the shops and restaurants at Fisherman's Wharf, this upscale hotel is 3 blocks from Ghirardelli Square, and 4.3 miles from the east end of Golden Gate Park. Modern rooms feature flat-screens, WiFi access (fee) and iPod docks, plus down comforters and marble bathrooms. Chic suites add separate living rooms and city views. Hypoallergenic rooms are also available. Amenities include 24-hour fitness facilities, an outdoor heated pool and a hot tub, plus a stylish restaurant, a business center and event space. Valet parking is available.

about.summary: This straightforward high-rise hotel is 1 mile from Union Square and the Civic Center BART station, 2 miles from Fisherman's Wharf, and 14 miles from San Francisco International Airport. Relaxed rooms have free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs, along with desks and minifridges. Suites have separate living areas and pull-out sofas. Kids stay with an adult for no charge. Evening room service is available. A casual restaurant serves California-inspired cuisine (kids 12 and under eat free). Other amenities include a bar, an outdoor heated pool and 24-hour gym, plus 18,000 sq ft of meeting space. Parking is available for a fee.

data.name: Hyatt Regency San Francisco
data.full_address: Hyatt Regency San Francisco, 5 Embarcadero Ctr, San Francisco, CA 94111

about.summary: Steps from the California Street cable car, this upscale downtown hotel with a soaring 17-story atrium is a 4-minute walk from the Ferry Plaza Building and its famous farmers market. Offering floor-to-ceiling windows with city or bay views, the laid-back rooms have 42-inch flat-screens, iPod docks and Wi-Fi access, as well as coffeemakers. Suites add sitting areas; club-level quarters provide access to a rooftop lounge serving complimentary breakfast and snacks. Amenities include a polished bar and a sleek modern restaurant serving Californian cuisine, plus a 24-hour exercise room. Extensive meeting and event space is available.

data.name: FOUND Hotel, San Francisco
data.full_address: FOUND Hotel, San Francisco, 140 Mason St, San Francisco, CA 94102

about.summary: Set in the Tenderloin neighborhood, this trendy, contemporary hotel is a 5-minute walk from Union Square and 3 minutes on foot from the Powell Street BART station. It's 2 miles from the famously steep Lombard Street. Private rooms feature flat-screen TVs and en suite bathrooms. There's a modern lobby lounge and a co-working space.

data.name: Fairmont San Francisco
data.full_address: Fairmont San Francisco, 950 Mason St, San Francisco, CA 94108

about.summary: Occupying a landmark Nob Hill building offering views of the city and the bay, this grand hotel is a 13-minute walk from Union Square, and 1.3 miles from the shops and restaurants at lively Pier 39. Polished rooms offer designer toiletries and Keurig coffeemakers, plus flat-screen TVs and Wi-Fi (fee); some have pull-out sofas and/or bay views. Plush suites add separate living areas; some have balconies, pool tables or wet bars. Room service is available. There's a fine-dining restaurant serving afternoon tea, a tiki bar with live entertainment, and a European-inspired cafe. Other amenities include a health club (fee) with trainers and a spa.

data.name: FOUND Hotel Carlton, Nob Hill
data.full_address: FOUND Hotel Carlton, Nob Hill, 1075 Sutter St, San Francisco, CA 94109

about.summary: A 13-minute walk from Union Square, this laid-back hotel in the Nob Hill neighborhood is an 11-minute walk from the Civic Center. Decorated with hand-painted Moroccan tables, marble-topped writing desks and global photography, the warm rooms feature free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs, Keurig coffeemakers and iPod docks. Upgraded rooms provide 42-inch TVs and city views, and a suite has a living room with a pull-out sofa, plus a soaking tub. An exotic fusion restaurant serves American breakfast, and freebies include nightly wine receptions with live music and local car service on weekday mornings. Valet parking is available for a fee.

data.name: Hilton San Francisco Financial District
data.full_address: Hilton San Francisco Financial District, 750 Kearny St, San Francisco, CA 94108

about.summary: Located in San Francisco's financial district, this upscale 27-story hotel is a 1-mile drive from conventions at the Moscone Center and 5 miles' drive from the Golden Gate Bridge. Offering city or bay views, the chic rooms have custom-designed beds, flat-screen TVs and Wi-Fi (fee). Upgraded rooms provide access to a club lounge with free breakfast and evening appetizers. Suites add living areas and minifridges. Room service is available. Amenities include a restaurant, a stylish bar, and a wine bar with access to iPads. A breakfast buffet is offered for a fee. There's also a 24/7 gym, a business center and 20,000 sq ft of meeting space.

data.name: Waterfront Hotel - JDV by Hyatt
data.full_address: Waterfront Hotel - JDV by Hyatt, 10 Washington St, Oakland, CA 94607

about.summary: Overlooking San Francisco Bay, this relaxed hotel is adjacent to Jack London Square and 1 mile from the Oakland Museum of California. It's also 3 miles from Crown Memorial State Beach. The nautical rooms feature free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs, iPod docks, and tea and coffeemakers. Some rooms offer balconies and/or harbor views. Suites add separate living spaces and/or fireplaces. Amenities include a heated outdoor pool, a sauna and an exercise room, as well as an Italian restaurant. Complimentary perks include weekday wine receptions and a local shuttle. There's also a 24-hour business center, along with 13 meeting rooms and valet parking (fee).

about.summary: This upscale hotel is a 6-minute walk from Fisherman's Wharf, 7 minutes on foot from Pier 39 and 16 miles from San Francisco International Airport. The refined rooms include Wi-Fi, flat-screens, minibars and coffeemakers. Upgraded rooms offer city views. Suites add separate living areas with pull-out sofas; some feature fireplaces. Room service is available. Amenities consist of morning coffee in the lobby, use of loaner bikes and iPads, as well as access to an off-site fitness center. There's a stylish bar and a trattoria-style restaurant. There's also a business center. Breakfast and parking are offered, and pets are welcome, all for a fee.

about.summary: Set in a beaux arts building in the Tenderloin area, this chic hotel dating from 1910 is 4 minutes' walk from Union Square, a mile from conventions at the Moscone Center, and an 8-minute walk from a BART station. The bright, retro-style rooms offer flat-screen TVs and free Wi-Fi, plus minibars and designer toiletries. Suites add separate living areas; some feature whirlpool tubs. In-room spa treatments are available. Freebies include loaner bikes, and morning coffee and evening wine served in a cozy lounge with a fireplace and live music. There's a trendy Italian restaurant and a 24-hour gym, as well as a business center and 13 meeting rooms.

data.name: Executive Inn & Suites
data.full_address: Executive Inn & Suites, 1755 Embarcadero, Oakland, CA 94606

about.summary: Set on the Brooklyn Basin, this casual waterfront hotel is 2 miles from Downtown Oakland's historic center and business district. It's also 9 miles from Oakland International Airport. Straightforward rooms feature flat-screen TVs, Wi-Fi, minifridges and microwaves. They also have private granite bathrooms with a combination tub/shower. All waterside rooms come with a balcony or deck. The hotel offers 5 meeting rooms, a heated outdoor swimming pool and a fitness room. There's also a restaurant. Breakfast and parking are available.

data.name: Hotel Zephyr San Francisco
data.full_address: Hotel Zephyr San Francisco, 250 Beach St, San Francisco, CA 94133

about.summary: A 3-minute walk from Pier 41 in the Fisherman's Wharf district on San Francisco Bay, this hip, nautical-themed hotel is a mile from the Exploratorium museum and 5 miles from the Golden Gate Bridge. Bright, sophisticated rooms offer free Wi-Fi and smart TVs, plus minifridges and coffeemakers. Upgraded rooms add balconies, some with bay and wharf views. The 1- and 2-bedroom suites feature floor-to-ceiling windows and sitting areas. Amenities include a colorful gym, and an airy, contemporary lounge/game room with a pool table, as well as a furnished terrace with fire pits, seating and sculptures. Parking is available for a fee.

data.name: HOTEL EPIK
data.full_address: HOTEL EPIK, 706 Polk St, San Francisco, CA 94109

about.summary: Set in a brick building near hip boutiques and buzzing bars, this funky hotel is an 11-minute walk from the closest BART station, a mile from Union Square and 2 miles from the famously crooked Lombard Street. Featuring parquet floors and bold, colorful accents, the modern rooms offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and iPod docks, plus Nespresso machines. Suites add separate living rooms with pull-out sofas. Amenities include a retro lobby lounge with board games and classic arcade games, along with a snack bar and a convenience store.

about.summary: Set in the buzzing Mid-Market neighborhood, this modern hotel is a 3-minute walk from Civic Center subway station, 6 minutes’ walk from the Asian Art Museum, and 3 miles from dining along Pier 39. The bright rooms feature city views and flat-screen TVs. Upgraded rooms add sitting areas. Amenities include a hip restaurant, a cafe, a gym and a 24-hour business center, plus meeting and event space. Pets are welcome.

about.summary: Overlooking San Francisco Bay, this low-key hostel is within 5 minutes' walk of bike paths, restaurants and multiple bus lines, and 1.5 miles from the Presidio. The simple accommodations include private rooms, and single-sex or mixed-gender dorms sleeping up to 10 people in bunk beds. Bathrooms are shared, and free Wi-Fi is available throughout. Complimentary perks include breakfast, bike storage and parking. There's a communal kitchen, a bistro and a bar. The hostel also offers a bright common area with high ceilings, a game and TV room, and a patio, plus laundry facilities (fees).
